<h2 id="having-trouble-with-the-middle-and-ring-fingers">Having trouble with the middle and ring fingers?</h2>

<p>When playing the bass notes, I strongly recommend using your middle and ring fingers (in addition to your index finger). While you technically can pull this off using <em>only</em> your index finger, itâ€™s a bad habit that I suggest avoiding. You need to train your weaker fingers (middle, ring, pinky) â€“ and though it can be frustrating at first it pays off later.</p>

<p>Hereâ€™s a simple exericse I suggest:</p>

